<p>The native resize handle of Safari for text areas does not have this bug. This bug is especially annoying, because the text areas of the site do not have the native resize handle of Safari   the site overrides it.</p>

<p>The bug also occurs when I am writing a question.</p>

<p>It would be nice to fix this bug. Thank you.</p>

